long_description    This package contains documents targetted \
                    for end-users of GNOME. See notes for a list \
                    of documents provided.

maintainers         nomaintainer
categories          gnome
license             CC-BY-SA-3
platforms           darwin
supported_archs     noarch
installs_libs       no
